description.en:
Robin Inu aims at being the first of its kind, a comic hero token. With the implementation of simple tokenomics and a straightforward marketing strategy, Robin aims to provide a safe space for traders.

Robin Mini game and NFTs will be a huge part of our ecosystem allowing users to play and earn tokens. Robin holders also get access to other projects with early access and decision-making when it comes to the next hero token that arises.
